main event: A report of a UFO sighting near Brooksville, Florida, on November 15, 1965.
interesting points: The UFO was described as glowing and round., The object was reported to have exploded when near the ground., Several reports of meteorites were received at the same time., A telephone call was made by a resident reporting the sighting near Weewahitchka, Florida., Investigators could not locate the witness or confirm further details.
witness description: a resident who called about the sighting
